linux (ubuntu):
sudo apt install nodejs
sudo apt install npm
sudo npm install discord.js
sudo npm install cowsay
sudo npm install forever
paste stuff from github in ~/
create auth.json should be something like:{"token":your_token_here_as_a_string} can be done with the comand echo{"token":your_token_here_as_a_string} > auth.json
to start: forever start bot.js

notes:
I recomend useing forever to run the bot as it crashes with the slightest network problom. forever will restart it automaticaly when this happens
